Subsetting Netcdf with rectangular region of interest (Ethiopia)¶

In [14]:
rfe = surface_rain.rfe
In [15]:
rfe_cliped = rfe.salem.subset(shape=shp_ethio)
In [16]:
rfe_cliped.salem.quick_map();

Maskout values within Ethiopia¶

In [17]:
rfe_et = rfe.salem.roi(shape=shp_ethio)
In [18]:
rfe_et.salem.quick_map();

Exporting the cliped dataset¶

In [19]:
rfe_et.to_netcdf('rfe_et.nc')
